    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2082,
      "versionNonce": 1191519433,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "hV67PIw34BPC8NSFJLGdn",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 453.4295477710532,
      "y": -78.86216470757364,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#fefefe",
      "width": 453.7596435546875,
      "height": 250,
      "seed": 2006866567,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767501416185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. Availability (data redundancy/async retries)\n-> i.e use queues\n2. Latency (caching data out of memory)\n-> Can use CDN for charity images/text\n3. Throughput (100 TPS)\n4. Consistency (Eventual consistency)\n-> read after write consistency (they should\nbe able to it in history right away)\n-> after write, read from write node\ntemporarily",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Availability (data redundancy/async retries)\n-> i.e use queues\n2. Latency (caching data out of memory)\n-> Can use CDN for charity images/text\n3. Throughput (100 TPS)\n4. Consistency (Eventual consistency)\n-> read after write consistency (they should\nbe able to it in history right away)\n-> after write, read from write node\ntemporarily",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a9",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 5412,
      "versionNonce": 2121769897,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "EFdDaWH95vMqeK-zgVflw",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": -57.04283250848144,
      "y": 316.3050557992188,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 449.99969482421875,
      "height": 200,
      "seed": 1933021737,
      "groupIds": [],
