      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767501416185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. 3 mil donations over 3 days (10^6 per day)\n-> can spike due to social media reach\n-> 10 TPS on average (but can be up to\n100 TPS)\n\n2. We want to should be able to handle 10\nTPS (up to 100 TPS) calls to our 3rd party\nvendor",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 3 mil donations over 3 days (10^6 per day)\n-> can spike due to social media reach\n-> 10 TPS on average (but can be up to\n100 TPS)\n\n2. We want to should be able to handle 10\nTPS (up to 100 TPS) calls to our 3rd party\nvendor",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aB",
      "autoResize": true
